metadata.name: Edge of death
metadata.description:
I knew a woman who loved the red color of her frozen cherries.  
I knew a woman who hated her red blood.  
I knew a woman who was deeply blue, but she was in love with red.  
I knew the woman who loved the high-heeled red shoes.  
I believe the color of "ending" is red, the color of "miss" and "death" are also red, maybe that is why people are attracted to red ... .
